With this application we will provide a friendly interface for finding information and obtaining books desired by the user. To do this, we provide an environment that integrates the best known and most useful in this field applications, such as Google Books and Maps for the acquisition or loan books or Wikipedia to expand knowledge about the authors and other works, curiosities , etc.
In three simple steps you can access all the possibilities onLibrary at your service. Just enter a keyword in the search box (like the name of a title or author) and will show all the information available about it. You can choose different editions of the same book or see the author's biography immediately. You can then click on "Map" to check the availability of libraries and nearest libraries, or access the purchase page on Google Books.
It also has the ability to read the freshest news about the book world by clicking on the "News" button and thus be up to date on the latest information about their favorite form of entertainment.
Finally, you have the possibility to share their experiences social networks to spread the use of books, which has declined among the population due to the powerful source of information is the Internet and the unstoppable thrust of social networks. Thus, they will become the standard user for many pieces of paper together in an openness to humanity, an explosion of fantasy ... or simply a quiet time.